    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >数字版预约特典：《女神异闻录5》服装＆BGM组合2</h2><br>《真·女神转生》系列中融入科幻世界观创作出的热门衍生作品《恶魔召唤师 灵魂骇客》诞生的第25个年头。继承了《恶魔召唤师》系列以及《灵魂骇客》的DNA，跨越四分之一个世纪，以进化的理念，描绘全新人物与科技的故事。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777620/extras/17abf0bf2dc410aa7bb1d88041460925.poster.avif?t=1763537332\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777620/extras/17abf0bf2dc410aa7bb1d88041460925.webm?t=1763537332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777620/extras/17abf0bf2dc410aa7bb1d88041460925.mp4?t=1763537332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777620/extras/083061619e377cd555c9af6203cd1aaf.poster.avif?t=1763537332\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777620/extras/083061619e377cd555c9af6203cd1aaf.webm?t=1763537332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777620/extras/083061619e377cd555c9af6203cd1aaf.mp4?t=1763537332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在不远的未来。世界面临着不为人知的毁灭危机。守护人类世界并超越人类认知的“Aion”分身--“林檎”与“菲格”，为了改变世界毁灭的命运，降临到人类世界。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777620/extras/f27b6dbafae15a1571a0f0293f10f1c4.poster.avif?t=1763537332\" width=616 height=346 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777620/extras/f27b6dbafae15a1571a0f0293f10f1c4.webm?t=1763537332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.